text: Gremuchy Klyuch () is a rural locality (a village) in Andreyevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 64 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo, 3 km from Andreyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Gremuchy Klyuch, Andreyevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
